'''Suzianna''' was the second [[wife]] of the Sumerian god [[Enlil]].<ref name="Fox1988">{{cite book|author=Michael V. Fox|title=Temple in society|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=eHjV2_-8V2oC&pg=PA8|accessdate=8 June 2011|year=1988|publisher=Eisenbrauns|isbn=978-0-931464-38-6|pages=8–}}</ref> Her shrine was recorded to be in the [[Ekur]].<ref name="Fox1988"/>

