'''Tongnaab''' ("Chief of the Earth") is a deity associated with the [[Tallensi|Tallensi people]] of northern [[Ghana]]. Tongnaab is particularly believed to have powers in fertility, stability and security.{{sfn|Allman|Parker|2005|p=3}}

The Tongnaab cult developed from a small regional belief in the [[Tallensi Traditional Area|Tong hills region]] before the colonial period, and gained substantial popularity as a witch-hunting deity during the colonial period, with followers across the [[Gold Coast (British colony)|Gold Coast]].{{sfn|Allman|Parker|2005|pp=5-6}}

